snippet.title: Flixet
snippet.description:
Welcome to FLIXET, where we put out latest trailers, reviews, mashups and news in and around the movie entertainment world
As the leading source of everything entertainment, Flixet brings to you the inside scoop on what's hot and happening in the movie business.

Turn on, tune in and get your all access pass by subscribing to our channel, turn the bell notification on and sharing it with the entire world. Do not be shy and drop in your comments on what you would like to watch on our channel where all biases are welcome
For the film family

Juiced by Flixet
